verses.pali:
Manopubbaṅgamā dhammā, manoseṭṭhā manomayā;
Manasā ce paduṭṭhena, bhāsati vā karoti vā;
Tato naṃ dukkhamanveti, cakkaṃva vahato padaṃ.

Manopubbaṅgamā dhammā, manoseṭṭhā manomayā;
Manasā ce pasannena, bhāsati vā karoti vā;
Tato naṃ sukhamanveti, chāyāva anapāyinī.

Subhānupassiṃ viharantaṃ, indriyesu asaṃvutaṃ;
Bhojanamhi cāmattaññuṃ, kusītaṃ hīnavīriyaṃ;
Taṃ ve pasahati māro, vāto rukkhaṃva dubbalaṃ.

Asubhānupassiṃ viharantaṃ, indriyesu susaṃvutaṃ;
Bhojanamhi ca mattaññuṃ, saddhaṃ āraddhavīriyaṃ;
Taṃ ve nappasahati māro, vāto selaṃva pabbataṃ.

Appampi ce saṃhita bhāsamāno, dhammassa hoti anudhammacārī;
Rāgañca dosañca pahāya mohaṃ, sammappajāno suvimuttacitto;
Anupādiyāno idha vā huraṃ vā, sa bhāgavā sāmaññassa hoti.

Pamādaṃ appamādena, yadā nudati paṇḍito;
Paññāpāsādamāruyha, asoko sokiniṃ pajaṃ;
Pabbatatṭhova bhummaṭṭhe, dhīro bāle avekkhati.

Mameva kataṃ maññantu, gihī pabbajitā ubho;
Mamevātivasā assu, kiccākiccesu kismici;
Iti bālassa saṅkappo, icchā māno ca vaḍḍhati.

Aññā hi lābhūpanisā, aññā nibbānagāminī;
Evametaṃ abhiññāya, bhikkhu buddhassa sāvako;
Sakkāraṃ nābhinandeyya, vivekamanubrūhaye.

Nidhīnaṃva pavattāraṃ, yaṃ passe vajjadassinaṃ;
Niggayhavādiṃ medhāviṃ, tādisaṃ paṇḍitaṃ bhaje;
Tādisaṃ bhajamānassa, seyyo hoti na pāpiyo.

Yesaṃ sambodhiyaṅgesu, sammā cittaṃ subhāvitaṃ;
Ādānapaṭinissagge, anupādāya ye ratā;
Khīṇāsavā jutimanto, te loke parinibbutā.

Yesaṃ sannicayo natthi, ye pariññātabhojanā;
Suññato animitto ca, vimokkho yesaṃ gocaro;
Ākāse va sakuṇtānaṃ, gati tesaṃ durannayā.

Yassāsavā parikkhīṇā, āhāre ca anissito;
Suññato animitto ca, vimokkho yassa gocaro;
Ākāse va sakuṇtānaṃ, padaṃ tassa durannayaṃ.

Māse māse sahas sena, yo yajetha sataṃ samaṃ;
Ekañca bhāvitattānaṃ, muhuttamapi pūjaye;
Sā ve pūjanā seyyo, yaṃ ce vassasataṃ hutaṃ.

Yo ca vassasataṃ jantu, aggiṃ paricare vane;
Ekañca bhāvitattānaṃ, muhuttamapi pūjaye;
Sā ve pūjanā seyyo, yaṃ ce vassasataṃ hutaṃ.

Mā'vamaññetha pāpassa, na mantaṁ āgamissati;
Udabindunipātena, udakumbho'pi pūrati;
Pūrati bālo pāpassa, thokaṁ thokaṁ pi ācinaṁ.

Mā'vamaññetha puññassa, na mantaṁ āgamissati;
Udabindunipātena, udakumbho'pi pūrati;
Pūrati dhīro puññassa, thokaṁ thokaṁ pi ācinaṁ.

Asso yathā bhadro kasāniviṭṭho, ātāpino saṃvegino bhavātha;
Saddhāya sīlena ca vīriyena ca, samādhinā dhammavinicchayena ca;
Sampannavijjācaraṇā satimanto, pahassatha dukkhamidaṃ anappakaṃ.

Gahakāraka diṭṭhosi, puna gehaṃ na kāhasi;
Sabbā te phāsukā bhaggā, gahakūṭaṃ visaṅkhataṃ;
Visaṅkhāragataṃ cittaṃ, taṇhānaṃ khayamajjhagā.

Yo sāsanaṃ ara hataṃ, ariyānaṃ dhammajīvinaṃ;
Paccosati dummedho, diṭṭhiṃ nissāya pāpikaṃ;
Phalāni kaṭṭhakasseva, attaghāñāya phullati.

Attanā va kataṃ pāpaṃ, attanā saṅkilissati;
Attanā akataṃ pāpaṃ, attanā va visujjhati;
Suddhi asuddhi paccattaṃ, nāñño aññaṃ visodhaye.

Na ve kadariyā devalokaṁ vajanti;
Bālā have nappasaṁsanti dānaṁ;
Dhīro ca dānaṁ anumodamāno,
Teneva so hoti sukhī parattha.

Anūpavādo anūpaghāto, pātimokkhe ca saṃvaro;
Mattaññutā ca bhattasmiṃ, pantañca sayanāsanaṃ;
Adhicitte ca āyogo, etaṃ buddhāna sāsanaṃ.

Bālasaṅgatacārī hi, dīghamaddhāna socati;
Dukkho bālehi saṁvāso, amitteneva sabbadā;
Dhīro ca sukhasaṁvāso, ñātīnaṁva samāgamo.

Tasmā hi, dhīrañca paññañca bahussutañca;
Dhorayhasīlaṁ vatavantamariyaṁ;
Taṁ tādisaṁ sappurisaṁ sumedhaṁ, bhajetha nakkhattapathaṁva candimā.

Porāṇametaṃ atula, netaṃ ajjatanāmiva;
Nindanti tuṇhimāsīnaṃ, nindanti bahubhāṇinaṃ;
Mitabhāṇimpi nindanti, natthi loke anindito.

Dadāti ve yathāsaddhaṁ, yathāpasādanaṁ jano;
Tattha ce maṅku bhavati, paresaṁ pānabhojane;
Na so divā vā rattiṁ vā, samādhiṁ adhigacchati.

Na tāvatā dhammadharo, yāvatā bahu bhāsati;
Yo ca appampi sutvāna, dhammaṁ kāyena passati;
Sa ve dhammadharo hoti, yo dhammaṁ nappamajjati.

Yogā ve jāyatī bhūrī, ayogā bhūrisaṅkhayo;
Etaṁ dvedhāpathaṁ ñatvā, bhavāya vibhavāya ca;
Tathāttānaṁ niveseyya, yathā bhūrī pavaḍḍhati.

Yesañca susamāraddhā, niccaṃ kāyagatā sati;
Akiccaṃ te na sevanti, kicce sātaccakārino;
Satānaṃ sampajānānaṃ, atthaṃ gacchanti āsavā.

Duppabbajjaṃ durabhiramaṃ, durāvāsā gharā dukhā;
Dukkhosamānasaṃvāso, dukkhānupatitaddhagū;
Tasmā na caddhagū siyā, na ca dukkhānupatito siyā.

Nagaraṁ yathā paccantaṁ, guttaṁ santarabāhiraṁ;
Evaṁ gopetha attānaṁ, khaṇo vo mā upaccagā;
Khaṇātītā hi socanti, nirayamhi samappitā.
